## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **neffy (epinephrine intranasal) 2023** = first FDA non-injection epinephrine. 70+ year IM auto-injector paradigm 후 first alternative route. ARS Pharmaceuticals 가 개발, 2 mg 단회 분무. needle phobia + auto-injector access barrier 해소. quantum-VQE 의 nasal mucosal absorption + β-AR direct fit.
2. **omalizumab (Xolair) 2024 food allergy** = first FDA omalizumab food allergy 1+세. anti-IgE mAb 가 asthma + chronic urticaria 후 food allergy paradigm 확장. OUtMATCH 임상시험 결과. quantum-VQE 의 Fcε-RI + IgE Fab interface 직접 fit.
3. **Palforzia 2020 peanut OIT** = first FDA peanut allergen oral immunotherapy 4-17세. OIT 의 first FDA 표준화. desensitization paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 IgE-allergen 결합 affinity modulation.
4. **avapritinib (Ayvakit) 2023 ISM** = first FDA indolent systemic mastocytosis. KIT D816V 표적. KIT pocket allosteric VQE 가 fit.
5. **epinephrine IM 0.3 mg = 70+ year 1L 표준** — auto-injector EpiPen + Auvi-Q + Adrenaclick + Symjepi 형식 변화 only, 분자 자체 변화 없음. neffy intranasal 이 first 분자 외 형식 변화.
6. **anti-histamine + corticosteroid + H2 antagonist = secondary** — anaphylaxis 1L 가 아니라 epinephrine 후 adjunct. biphasic anaphylaxis prevention 의 corticosteroid evidence limited.
7. **glucagon = β-blocker-related anaphylaxis** — β-blocker 사용 환자의 epinephrine refractory anaphylaxis 응급. cAMP 직접 활성화.
8. **venom immunotherapy + SLIT = chronic desensitization** — SCIT venom (insect sting) + SLIT (Grastek + Ragwitek + Oralair) — chronic 면역 modulation paradigm.
9. **K-anaphylaxis + 식약처 framework + 한국 K-EpiPen** — 한국 임상 K-pharma framework + ARS Pharmaceuticals neffy 의 K-import potential. 식약처 표준 framework cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, anaphylaxis 임상 의미 한정. epinephrine pharmacology 70+ year, 변화 가 paradigm 형식 (intranasal) + 표적 expansion (anti-IgE food allergy + KIT ISM) 중심.

